I"D	<p><strong>Medium humanoid (kuo-toa), neutral evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 13 (natural armor, unarmored defense)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 65 (10d8+20)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 33 ft., swim 30 ft.</p>

